'''''Star Wars Insider'' 67''' is the sixty-seventh issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine. It was released to newsstands on [[April 15]], [[2003]]. The subscriber-exclusive edition of issue 67 included the third volume of ''[[Bantha Tracks (department)|Bantha Tracks]]'', the [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Official ''Star Wars'' Fan Club]] newsletter. This issue also came packaged with a special poster to commemorate the twentieth anniversary of the [[original trilogy]] film [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']].

