===Features===
*"[[Prequel Update]]" {{C|by [[Dave Gross]]}}
*:<small>Don't believe anything you read on the Internet, warns [[Rick McCallum]]. Again.</small>
*"[[The Ultimate Return of the Jedi Insider's Guide|The Ultimate ''Return of the Jedi Insider''{{'s}} Guide]]" {{C|by [[Daniel Wallace]]}}
*:<small>One hundred things you didn't know about [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|Episode VI]].</small>
*"[[Beyond the Valley of the Ewoks]]" {{C|by [[Eric Moro]]}}
*:<small>Once the smallest [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] of them all, [[Warwick Davis]] has used his fame to help little actors get noticed.</small>
*"[[Who's Who in the Max Rebo Band]]" {{C|by [[Rich Handley]]}}
*:<small>[[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba's]] favorite house band played its first gig long before working for the slimy crime lord.</small>
*"[[FX Karma: Pickle Ships, Tennis Shoes, and Other Untold Tales of the Return of the Jedi Space Battle|FX Karma: Pickle Ships, Tennis Shoes, and Other Untold Tales of the ''Return of the Jedi'' Space Battle]]" {{C|by [[Ron Magid]]}}
*:<small>[[Ken Ralston]] supervised one of the most heated space battles ever to appear on the silver screen. His secret? Tennis shoes and bubble gum.</small>
*"[[Seeking Revenge: A Collector's History of Revenge of the Jedi|Seeking Revenge: A Collector's History of ''Revenge of the Jedi'']]" {{C|by [[Pete Vilmur]]}}
*:<small>''Star Wars'' collectors help unravel the urban legends surrounding Episode VI's pre-release name change.</small>
*"[[The Trouble with Squibs]]" {{C|by [[Troy Denning]]}}
*:<small>After the events of ''[[Tatooine Ghost]]'', [[Han Solo/Legends|Han]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia]] do a little art shopping, Solo style.</small>
*"[[Insider Interview]]: Lama Su" {{C|by [[Kevin Rubio]]}}
*:<small>Kevin seeks expert advice on cloning for fun and profit and is introduced to the [[Clone trooper/Legends|Clone trooper]] known as [[CT-282-SD00001-983725138|282]].</small>

